src/occ.py 		- main module, handles events, config reading/saving
src/layout.py		- module responsible for rendering layout
src/rendering.py	- module for rendering on PiTFT display
src/ride_parameters.py	- all ride parameters read from sensors are handled here
src/gps_mtk3339.py	- module to talk to gps and parse data received from gps
src/bmp183.py		- module for handling pressure and temperature reading from bmp183 sensor
src/test_bmp183.py	- test modules for bmp183 sensor
src/test_gps.py		- test modules for gps hardware

